327
00:20:22,096 --> 00:20:23,461
"Imala me je."

328
00:20:23,531 --> 00:20:25,293
"Nije bilo sumlje u vezi toga."

329
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:29,601
"Ona nije bila kao
devojke iz"Ksavijara"."

330
00:20:31,339 --> 00:20:33,135
"Ali to je ono to me
je odvuklo ka njoj."

331
00:20:42,115 --> 00:20:43,343
Sedi.

332
00:21:23,088 --> 00:21:25,921
Sviraj.
Sviraj Baha.

333
00:21:45,977 --> 00:21:47,501
Pogledaj u mene.

334
00:21:54,486 --> 00:21:56,454
Njeno lice
zrai snagom.

335
00:21:59,424 --> 00:22:01,415
"Postao sam
zavisan od nje."

336
00:22:07,732 --> 00:22:08,925
"Njene nemirne oi...

337
00:22:10,334 --> 00:22:11,768
su me izazivale."

338
00:22:18,141 --> 00:22:19,904
"To je udna stvar,
kada se desi...

339
00:22:19,977 --> 00:22:22,310
da se umetnik i
subjekat potpuno sloe."

340
00:22:25,115 --> 00:22:27,015
"Stvorena je energija sunca."

341
00:22:30,921 --> 00:22:32,912
"Svako ulo koje
imaju igra ulogu...

342
00:22:32,990 --> 00:22:35,151
u neemu to je
veoma snano."

343
00:22:46,870 --> 00:22:48,837
"Ali to se ne govori."

344
00:22:52,643 --> 00:22:55,476
"Reci to naglas i
mogao bi ga ubiti."

345
00:23:15,197 --> 00:23:16,789
Hey!

346
00:23:16,866 --> 00:23:18,458
Hoe jo da fotografie?

347
00:23:18,534 --> 00:23:20,001
Svakako.

348
00:23:20,069 --> 00:23:22,263
Nai emo se kod
mene posle kole.

349
00:23:39,521 --> 00:23:42,183
Mogao bih da te
fotografiem svaki dan.

350
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:53,664
ta misli ovako?

351
00:23:56,104 --> 00:23:57,071
