O emu ste priali?

403
00:26:50,840 --> 00:26:52,831
Nekim fotografijama koje
sam hteo da mu pokaem.

404
00:26:52,909 --> 00:26:54,934
Veoma zanimljivo.

405
00:26:55,011 --> 00:26:56,569
Moram da idem.
Moram da idem!

406
00:26:56,646 --> 00:26:57,634
Poljubi me.

407
00:26:57,713 --> 00:26:59,374
Moram da idem.

408
00:26:59,449 --> 00:27:01,440
Shay.
Shay!

409
00:27:36,018 --> 00:27:37,882
Dobro.Gledaj
pravo u mene.

410
00:27:39,921 --> 00:27:42,686
Savreno.
Savreno.

