423
00:28:40,347 --> 00:28:43,544
To sam ve znala.Rekla sam
reci mi neto to niko ne zna.

424
00:28:43,617 --> 00:28:45,346
Plai me i
svidja mi se.

425
00:28:47,854 --> 00:28:49,481
